'''Buccaneer''' was a rank in the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]]' system of ranks. Buccaneers were second-in-command to the [[Pirate King/Legends|Pirate King]] or Queen and would often be in direct command of the [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]]. They also served as assistants and advisors to the King or Queen.

